Communicated by:
ProMED-mail
<promed@promedmail.org>

[The key to controlling these outbreaks revolves around changing the paradigm of HAV prevention. In addition to vaccination of critical cohorts such as food service workers, addressing the homeless and providing appropriate care for drug users are useful interventions.

